Kapsch Sees Russia Tendering Toll Systems, Wirschaftsblatt Says

-- B y   Z o e   S c h n e e w e i s s
-- 
2011-04-12T05:35:39Z

-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2011-04-12/kapsch-sees-russia-tendering-toll-systems-wirschaftsblatt-says.html
Kapsch TrafficCom AG (KTCG) , an Austrian
maker of toll road systems, expects  Russia  to tender electronic
toll systems in the next one or two years, Wirtschaftsblatt
reported, citing the company’s Russia head.  About 2,000 kilometers of roads could be tolled, Kapsch’s
Michael Weber told the Vienna-based paper.  To contact the editor responsible for this story:
Zoe Schneeweiss at 
 zschneeweiss@bloomberg.net  